HTML Select Element Binder
My name Gabriel Pires (http://gabrielpires.com.br) and I create this script to make easy my days as web-developer.
This is a javascript that work to bind with ajax a select HTML element.
You can find a simple documentation in docs folder and 2 samples in samples folder.

//HTML SELECT BINDER
//Author: Gabriel Pires - gabrielpires.com.br
//Version: 1.0
//Release Date: 2010-09-01
//The ajax handler is Ajax Requester - MyLib JS - Developed by David Mark - http://www.cinsoft.net/